caption: Figure 4 Example of network with five phenotypes and three QTL (Panel a), and the expected output of single-trait QTL analyses for such phenotypes (Panel b). On Panel b, dashed and pointed arrows represent direct and indirect effects of QTLs on phenotypes, respectively.
